Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Carter vetoes defence bill
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b040bt88
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 27 Aug 1978
President Carter vetoes defence bill. Objects to proposed $2 billion nuclear aircraft carrier. The sound quality on this recording is variable/poor. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014. Show less